  "remarks": "\nOd Yosef Chai yeshiva (hereafter “OD YOSEF CHAI”) is an involved person within the meaning of the Global Human Rights Sanctions Regulations 2020 on the basis of the following ground: OD YOSEF CHAI \nis and/or has been facilitating, inciting or providing support for activity which amounts to a serious abuse of the right of individuals not to be subjected to cruel, inhuman or degrading treatment or punishment.\n",
